                    <p>Short term rental (STR) management is the professional handling of properties listed on platforms like Airbnb, VRBO, and Booking.com. In Toronto, STR management has become increasingly complex due to municipal regulations, making professional management more valuable than ever.</p>
                    
                    <p>Unlike <a href="/services/mid-term-rental-management-toronto" style="color: var(--sage-dark);">mid-term rental management</a> (30+ days), short term rentals involve stays under 28 nights and require specific licensing in Toronto and the Greater Toronto Area. Our team handles all aspects of STR operations so you can maximize revenue while staying compliant.</p>

